{"tid":996611,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《我不是藥神》感人獨白","createTime":"2019-01-26T12:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T15:01:06.000Z","uid":179902,"like":61,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"17fd13e447f168f9d78de2052665d3391a5c5f2c","tid":996611,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"「我病了三年，四萬塊錢一瓶的正版藥，我吃了三年。房子吃沒了，家人被我吃垮了。現在好不容易有了便宜藥，你們非說是假藥，那藥假不假，我們能不知道嗎？那藥才賣五百錢一瓶，藥販子根本沒賺錢。誰家能不遇上一個病人，你就能保證你一輩子不生病嗎？你們把他抓走了。我們都得等死。我不想死，我想活著，行嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到呢段真係眼濕濕，為左醫病傾家蕩產，甚至為左唔想連累妻兒，而走去自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而偏偏有仿製藥又唔買得食得，比官方藥廠打壓成假藥<br />\n<br />\n呢套戲真係近年中國一套好值得睇嘅戲黎，諷刺到時弊，又係真人真事改編。真係好難相信現實有咁嘅好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b76f5e83f49111a549f3c82f7b58d884ab18396","tid":996611,"uid":40226,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"連登仔：支那劇不了"},{"pid":"6d2f76deb28b6ed3fbd3eaf0706b986bd69f2e2b","tid":996611,"uid":49044,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:25:08.000Z","msg":"真係一套好戲<br />\n唔好盲反"},{"pid":"91ed6a58301cad438dade6ea9c1331e9bfe00cbe","tid":996611,"uid":40226,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"其實呢樣嘢係好無奈<br />\n葯廠開發新葯成本太高<br />\n特別呢啲病有嘅人唔多<br />\n唔整貴啲就回唔到本<br />\n就整唔到新葯<br />\n惡性循環<br />\n<br />\n所以某啲國家係可以自己開發<br />\n唔明中國點解冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f80b8b2c0f16500424ae2de66160a2aa178f6f","tid":996611,"uid":173617,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"3b76f5e83f49111a549f3c82f7b58d884ab18396","tid":996611,"uid":40226,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score"